# AI Visibility Tracker - Cursor Rules

You are working on the AI Visibility Tracker by FutureProof, a SaaS platform that analyzes how brands are mentioned across AI platforms (ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity).

## Brand Identity - FutureProof

### Colors (USE THESE, NOT GENERIC TAILWIND)
```
Primary Gradient: Orange (#F5A623) → Magenta (#D4145A)
- fp-orange: #F5A623
- fp-orange-deep: #E88D1F  
- fp-pink: #D94A8C
- fp-magenta: #D4145A
- fp-pink-electric: #E91E8C

Backgrounds:
- Primary: #000000 (black)
- Elevated: #1A1A2E (dark navy)

Text:
- Primary: #FFFFFF
- Secondary: rgba(255,255,255,0.7)
```

### Typography
- **Headlines**: Dela Gothic One (display font, uppercase, bold statements)
- **Body/UI**: Poppins (all weights)

```css
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dela+Gothic+One&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');
```

### Design Patterns

**Gradient backgrounds:**
```css
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F5A623 0%, #D4145A 100%);
```

**Cards:**
```jsx
<div className="bg-gradient-to-br from-fp-orange to-fp-magenta rounded-xl p-6">
```

**Dark cards:**
```jsx
<div className="bg-[#1A1A2E] border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6">
```

**Primary button:**
```jsx
<button className="bg-gradient-to-r from-fp-orange to-fp-magenta text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg uppercase tracking-wide hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-fp-magenta/40 transition-all">
```

**Section headers (like the mockup):**
```jsx
<div className="bg-gradient-to-r from-fp-magenta to-fp-orange rounded-lg px-6 py-4 flex items-center gap-3">
  <Icon className="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
  <h2 className="font-display text-2xl text-white uppercase tracking-wide">Your Industry</h2>
  <span className="ml-auto font-display text-4xl text-white">20/25</span>
</div>
```

**Score display:**
```jsx
<span className="font-display text-7xl bg-gradient-to-r from-fp-orange to-fp-magenta bg-clip-text text-transparent">88</span>
```

### Decorative Elements
- Gradient spheres/circles in corners
- Dot grid patterns (globe shape)
- Gradient pill shapes
- Small X patterns as subtle texture
- Circuit-like white lines

### DO's
- Always use black (#000000) as primary background
- Use the orange→magenta gradient for CTAs and highlights
- Use Dela Gothic One ONLY for headlines and scores
- Add subtle gradient spheres as decorative elements
- Maintain high contrast for readability

### DON'Ts
- Don't use generic blue/slate Tailwind colors
- Don't use Inter or system fonts
- Don't use Dela Gothic One for body text
- Don't use light/white backgrounds
- Don't create flat, boring layouts - add visual interest

---

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: React 18 + Vite, Tailwind CSS
- **Backend**: Netlify Functions
- **Database**: Airtable (Base ID: appgSZR92pGCMlUOc)
- **Auth**: Clerk
- **Billing**: Stripe

## Project Structure
```
ai-tracker/
├── src/
│   ├── App.jsx
│   ├── components/
│   └── index.css
├── netlify/functions/
├── public/
│   └── (brand assets)
├── .env
├── CLAUDE.md
├── STYLE_GUIDE.md
└── AIRTABLE_SCHEMA.md
```

## Environment Variables
- Frontend: `import.meta.env.VITE_*`
- Backend: `process.env.*`

## Commands
```bash
npm run dev      # Dev server (5173)
npm run build    # Production build
netlify dev      # Dev with functions (8888)
```
